Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 糟糕 睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是报社的休刊日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街道也因为盂兰盆节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与往常不同的显得很安静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得真是很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是盂兰盆节了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:30.89,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(870,560)\fad(500,100)\be1}第一次的 迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就做早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样 春华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只喝酒不吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会喝坏胃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 下酒菜的话有很不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挡住挡住挡住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天绝赞的下酒菜是这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查阅点 花园町的的高速公路出入口的50千米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央道以相模湖町为中心持续着45千米的塞车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好可以下酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是下酒菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这车列里有很多的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们一定都在或者忍着不能去上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者生气撒着娇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 漏出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 说了要给我买点心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说明什么 春华
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向和梦她们还没起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说睡懒觉也是她们的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却只会让明天变得更辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向好像已经起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为房间里有发出嘎吱嘎吱的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可爱小硬币们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭和40年出生的100日元的硬币不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向日葵的花语是虚伪的富贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼里只看得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是在打扫卫生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把有梦和有纪叫起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腻了的话就会起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腻了的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好有纪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该起来了还是再睡会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再睡会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行呀 痒痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 梦也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天午饭做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（学马奔跑的动作和声音）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 盂兰盆节
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话可以让我点燃迎魂火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈那边的盂兰盆节是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上在玄关用麻秆点燃迎魂火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮豆腐渣？ 在玄关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你大概搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻秆是种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 干干的白白的长长的秆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在地上或是锅里烧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊列
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篝火晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说迎魂火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后是把素斋呀水果之类的摆好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一样的好好做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像加奈家里做过的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真对待传统活动也是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把那张画当作没发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多事情全部都当作没发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起合力让盂兰盆节的气氛高涨起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想把输牌当作没发生过是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 把人说的那么坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就好好的出牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我干嘛不出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 梦和有纪负责食物材料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向负责采购花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈和春华一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把盂兰盆的祭坛准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想奶奶知不知道我在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我要是奶奶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的孙女在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吃着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能不去想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈在这里哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天穿的是什么内裤之类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天胸部的情况怎么样之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有圆圆屁股之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揉啊揉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代理那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中元节收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我顺便来帮你摆放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是顺便顺便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有牌位和遗像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以前上美术馆课时画的肖像画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个画的能让人看懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个是因为画的有点慌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真面画的话可以画的很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这个花像是柏青哥店开店时用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又很华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那并不是值得自满的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该开始点迎魂火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要用茄子做的马先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs-4}在日本有点燃迎魂灯后，便可以让插着四根牙签的茄子变成牛，黄瓜变成马，\N驮着祖先的灵魂早日回家的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是马 是牛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄瓜是马先生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茄子是奶牛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的盂兰盆节不就是像这样迎接已逝的人回来的仪式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以迎接的人怀着“快点回来啊”的心情\N就准备了跑得比较快的马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以相反
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送祖先回去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能慢慢的回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就准备的是牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得春春好像是老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走过这个街道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶能早点回来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为担心这加奈就一直在身边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的笨笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是发着傻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶也不能放手不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春春奶奶我也对加奈担心的担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在担心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盂兰盆会舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是盂兰盆节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呢呢 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的盂兰盆会舞会开很多商店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是祭典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能把煮菜的火还开着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮菜的火看起来好像是没问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈喜欢祭典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为经常和奶奶一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家又一起去盂兰盆会舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选自己喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈也选件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个是谁的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里人员流动比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就堆积了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向日葵花样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又很有夏天的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个花火图案怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百合之类的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我选这个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得有点孩子气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苹果糖 巧克力 香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边还有棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零花钱每个人1000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有1000日元这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可以当作特别费使用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
