Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就算是赞同了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想捞金鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相当擅长呢
