Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有要瞄准我的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手春华
