Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为混在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次会不会变成紫色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
