Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不注意前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好看着前面走路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要柠檬汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该好好道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么姐姐要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是烤章鱼 烤章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叽叽叽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代理她们在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 红蜻蜓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
