Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好看着前面走路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好的看着前面走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊列什么啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代理 春华
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微一不看着你就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底做了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞到了个不认识的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识的孩子是指她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是青蛙
