Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家大家不都是普通小麦粉做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要点送别火了快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次的 回忆谈话
